headline: Ukraine is Upending the Global Oil Market. Here’s Who Benefits.
summary: Ukraine has found a new way to disrupt Russia’s economy, and it’s scrambling the global oil market.  The biggest winners so far are refiners such as  Valero  and  Marathon Petroleum  which are profiting from wider profit margins on products like gasoline and diesel.  Ukraine has been attacking Russian refineries with drones as the war drags on.
